{"tid":1490822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"義士被控襲擊中國藉男子？！？！","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:12:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:19:05.000Z","uid":48885,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e779e08015e391a4b11c42e48bc205a7890cf384","tid":1490822,"uid":48885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190820/mobile/bkn-20190820150421933-0820_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190820%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190820150421933-0820_00822_001.html&d=QZ1X7Ww%2BB3pe%2FYPW%2Fe6VuRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=4e3ceddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190820/mobile/bkn-20190820150421933-0820_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n上月14日沙田遊行後，新城市廣場內爆發警方與示威者激烈衝突，多人被捕。其中一名被捕人士為49歲龔志遠，報稱保安員，被控兩項非法集結及一項意圖傷人罪。案件今日在東區裁判法院提訊，他暫時毋須答辯，控方不反對被告保釋，案件現押後下月16日等警方進一步調查再訊，期間被告准以3000港元保釋，但不得離港及不得進入沙田新城市廣場等。 <br />\n<br />\n被告龔志遠被控於今年7月14日，在沙田新城市廣場連同其他身份不明人士非法集結，同時連同其他身份不明人士，意圖使一名中國籍男子身體受嚴重傷害而非法及惡意傷人。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係中國藉男子而唔係黑警，好可疑，係唔係公安？"},{"pid":"bb5234b9da6b3413525cfb805f02c727fccf9675","tid":1490822,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:14:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56fb8284b76ec994c5ca03ac8de16b0ed4da4ea7","tid":1490822,"uid":62032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n邊道跑個大陸人出嚟"},{"pid":"cf139542d084d8efff590ac138d69a2db8dced64","tid":1490822,"uid":21002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e779e08015e391a4b11c42e48bc205a7890cf384","tid":1490822,"uid":48885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/b